Package: exvar
Title: Visualization and Analysis of Gene Expression and Genomic Variants
Version: 1.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Imraan", "Dixon", , "imraandixon@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5399-5182"))
    person("Hiba", "Ben Aribi", , "benaribi.hiba@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9547-8725"))
Description: Enables easy and streamlined visualization of analytical
    functionality for biologists with limited computational skills. It supports
    alignment of FASTQ files to a reference genome, SNP, indel, and CNV calling,
    as well as generating gene count information and performing differential
    expression analysis. Additionally, it has built-in GUI functionality for
    visualizing these data.
